---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
  <BaseHead
    title="律师费用说明 | 何淼律师 — Ontario 家庭法"
    description="何淼律师收费透明，提供初次咨询、无争议离婚、协议起草及诉讼代理服务。初次咨询30分钟$220+HST。647-930-6688。"
  />
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "ProfessionalService",
    "@id": "https://www.miaohelaw.ca/#lawfirm",
    "name": "Miao He (何淼) — Ontario Family Law Lawyer",
    "url": "https://www.miaohelaw.ca",
    "telephone": "+1-647-930-6688",
    "priceRange": "$$",
    "hasOfferCatalog": {
      "@type": "OfferCatalog",
      "name": "法律服务收费",
      "itemListElement": [
        {
          "@type": "Offer",
          "itemOffered": {
            "@type": "Service",
            "name": "初次咨询",
            "description": "30分钟初次法律咨询，中英双语，面谈或视频均可。"
          },
          "price": "220",
          "priceCurrency": "CAD"
        },
        {
          "@type": "Offer",
          "itemOffered": {
            "@type": "Service",
            "name": "无争议离婚",
            "description": "双方就离婚条件达成一致，何律师协助完成全部法律文件及法院申请程序。"
          },
          "priceSpecification": {
            "@type": "PriceSpecification",
            "minPrice": "2000",
            "maxPrice": "3500",
            "priceCurrency": "CAD"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Offer",
          "itemOffered": {
            "@type": "Service",
            "name": "协议起草",
            "description": "婚前协议、分居协议、同居协议的专业起草服务，3个月内签署完毕无额外费用。"
          },
          "priceSpecification": {
            "@type": "PriceSpecification",
            "minPrice": "2500",
            "maxPrice": "4500",
            "priceCurrency": "CAD"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  }
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <Header />
  <main class="page-main">

    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="page-hero-inner">
        <div class="page-label">律师费用说明 · LEGAL FEES</div>
        <h1>收费透明，没有隐藏费用</h1>
        <p>我相信客户在决定是否聘请律师之前，有权利了解大概的费用范围。以下是我的主要服务收费说明。所有费用均需另加 HST，部分服务另有 disbursements（垫付费用）。</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pricing-section">
      <div class="pricing-inner">

        <div class="pricing-card highlight">
          <div class="pricing-tag">最常见的第一步</div>
          <h2>初次咨询</h2>
          <div class="pricing-amount">$220 <span>+ HST</span></div>
          <div class="pricing-detail">30分钟 · 中英双语 · 面谈或视频均可</div>
          <p>法律问题没有标准答案。在初次咨询中，我不只听案情，更会为你拆解全局。</p>
          <p>我会为你揭开诉讼的迷雾，分析每一种可能的博弈策略——明确告知你诉讼的风险点、谈判的筹码，以及推进的最优路径。很多客户在咨询后告诉我，最让他们心安的是终于"看清了全局"。</p>
          <p>我拒绝让客户在模糊中仓促进入诉讼。我的目标是确保你在掌握完整策略的基础上，做出最理智的选择。</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#9A8060;">咨询费按每6分钟一个计费单元收取，30分钟为一次完整咨询。</p>
          <a href="tel:6479306688" class="btn-primary">📞 立即预约 647-930-6688</a>
        </div>

        <h2 class="section-subtitle">固定费用服务</h2>
        <p class="section-note">以下服务提供固定费用范围，费用因案件具体情况而有所不同。所有费用均需另加 HST 及 disbursements。</p>

        <div class="pricing-grid">

          <div class="pricing-card">
            <h3>无争议离婚</h3>
            <div class="pricing-amount-sm">$2,000 – $3,500 <span>+ HST + disbursements</span></div>
            <p>适用于双方就离婚条件已达成一致的情况。我们不是只负责起草文件就完事的律师——从文件准备到法院递交，到主动跟进法院处理进度，直到你拿到离婚证，全程由我们负责，不需要你自己去追。</p>
            <p>只要双方保持配合、中途没有变成争议离婚，固定费用内不会产生额外收费。你不需要担心中途被追加账单。</p>
            <div class="pricing-includes">
              <div class="includes-title">全程包含：</div>
              <ul>
                <li>审查双方协议内容，确认符合法律要求</li>
                <li>准备并递交所有法院文件</li>
                <li>主动跟进法院处理进度，无需客户自行追踪</li>
                <li>取得离婚令（Divorce Order）及离婚证（Divorce Certificate）</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="pricing-note">⚠️ 如对方中途不配合或案件演变为争议离婚，费用另行讨论。</div>
          </div>

          <div class="pricing-card">
            <h3>协议起草</h3>
            <div class="pricing-amount-sm">$2,500 – $4,500 <span>+ HST + disbursements</span></div>
            <p>适用于需要起草婚前协议、婚内协议、分居协议或同居协议的情况。我以诉讼律师的视角起草协议，预判漏洞，确保协议具有法律效力。</p>
            <div class="pricing-includes">
              <div class="includes-title">包含：</div>
              <ul>
                <li>全面了解双方财务状况及诉求</li>
                <li>起草完整协议文本</li>
                <li>协助完成签署程序（ILA）</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="pricing-note">✅ 3个月内完成签署，不额外收费。超出部分按时间计费。</div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <h2 class="section-subtitle">诉讼代理</h2>

        <div class="pricing-card">
          <h3>家庭法诉讼全程代理</h3>
          <div class="pricing-amount-sm">按小时计费 <span>每6分钟为一计费单元</span></div>
          <p>适用于争议性离婚、财产分割、子女监护权争夺、配偶赡养费、跨境资产追索等需要在法院进行的案件。</p>
          <p>费用因案件复杂程度、庭审频率及所需工作量而异。每一份文件、每一次上庭、每一封邮件都会如实记录在账单中，不设隐藏收费。</p>
          <div class="pricing-includes">
            <div class="includes-title">计费范围包括：</div>
            <ul>
              <li>法庭出席及庭前准备</li>
              <li>动议文件起草及答辩</li>
              <li>与对方律师的沟通协商</li>
              <li>调解及庭外和解谈判</li>
              <li>客户沟通及法律意见</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="section-subtitle">Limited Retainer · 有限委托</h2>

        <div class="pricing-card">
          <h3>什么是 Limited Retainer？</h3>
          <div class="pricing-amount-sm">按实际工作量计费</div>
          <p>Limited Retainer（有限委托）是指客户不将整个案件全权交给律师，而是只委托律师处理案件中的特定事项。委托协议会明确列出代理范围，代理事项完成后，委托自动终止。</p>
          <p>适合以下情况：</p>
          <div class="pricing-includes">
            <ul>
              <li>客户选择自行代理（Self-represented），但需要律师协助准备特定文件或走法庭程序</li>
              <li>客户需要律师出席某一次庭审或会议，但不需要全程代理</li>
              <li>客户需要律师审查对方提交的文件或协议，提供书面法律意见</li>
              <li>案件已进入尾声，只需要律师协助完成最后的法律程序</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <p>有限委托让客户在控制费用的同时，在关键节点获得专业的法律支持。如果你正在考虑自行代理但不确定某些步骤，欢迎咨询是否适合这种安排。</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="section-subtitle">关于 Disbursements（垫付费用）</h2>

        <div class="pricing-card">
          <p>Disbursements 是律师在处理案件过程中代客户垫付的第三方费用，与律师费分开计算，在账单中单独列明。</p>
          <div class="pricing-includes">
            <div class="includes-title">安省法院官方收费（Ontario Superior Court of Justice）</div>
            <ul>
              <li>申请书归档费（Application filing）— <strong>$224</strong></li>
              <li>离婚宣誓书归档费（Affidavit for Divorce filing）— <strong>$445</strong></li>
              <li>离婚证书申请费（Divorce Certificate）— <strong>$25</strong></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="pricing-includes" style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">
            <div class="includes-title">其他常见 Disbursements</div>
            <ul>
              <li>送达费用（Process Server）</li>
              <li>文件公证及认证费</li>
              <li>专家报告费（如企业估值 CBV、财务评估）</li>
              <li>翻译及口译费用</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <p>以上法院收费为安省现行标准，如有调整以法院公告为准。所有 disbursements 均会在账单中如实列明，不会有任何隐藏收费。</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="page-cta">
      <h2>有费用相关问题？</h2>
      <p>每个案件情况不同。欢迎预约初次咨询，我会根据你的具体情况给出费用估算。</p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="tel:6479306688" class="btn-primary">📞 647-930-6688</a>
        <a href="mailto:miao@miaohelaw.ca" class="btn-secondary">miao@miaohelaw.ca</a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</body>
</html>

<style>
  .page-main { max-width: 100%; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .page-hero { background: #2C2418; padding: 4rem 2rem; text-align: center; }
  .page-hero-inner { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .page-label { font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9A8060; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .page-hero h1 { font-family: 'Georgia', serif; font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: 400; color: #FAC775; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .page-hero p { color: #C4AA80; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .pricing-section { padding: 4rem 2rem; }
  .pricing-inner { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .section-subtitle { font-family: 'Georgia', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 400; color: #1A1208; margin: 3rem 0 0.5rem; padding-bottom: 0.75rem; border-bottom: 2px solid #EDE8DF; }
  .section-note { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #9A8060; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .pricing-card { background: #FDFBF7; border: 1px solid #EDE8DF; border-radius: 8px; padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; border-left: 4px solid #7A5A1A; }
  .pricing-card.highlight { border-left-color: #FAC775; background: #2C2418; }
  .pricing-card.highlight h2 { color: #FAC775; font-family: 'Georgia', serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .pricing-card.highlight p { color: #C4AA80; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.8; }
  .pricing-tag { font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9A8060; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .pricing-amount { font-family: 'Georgia', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; color: #FAC775; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .pricing-amount span { font-size: 1rem; color: #9A8060; }
  .pricing-detail { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #9A8060; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .pricing-card h3 { font-family: 'Georgia', serif; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 400; color: #1A1208; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .pricing-amount-sm { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: #7A5A1A; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .pricing-amount-sm span { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 400; color: #9A8060; }
  .pricing-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #4A3A2A; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .pricing-includes { background: #F5EFE0; border-radius: 6px; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; margin: 1rem 0; }
  .includes-title { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; color: #7A5A1A; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .pricing-includes ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.25rem; }
  .pricing-includes li { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #4A3A2A; line-height: 1.8; }
  .pricing-note { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #6B5A3A; margin-top: 0.75rem; padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem; background: rgba(122,90,26,0.06); border-radius: 4px; }
  .pricing-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .btn-primary { display: inline-block; background: #7A5A1A; color: #FDFBF7; padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 1.25rem; }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: #4A3A0A; color: #FDFBF7; }
  .page-cta { background: #F5EFE0; border-top: 1px solid #EDE8DF; padding: 4rem 2rem; text-align: center; }
  .page-cta h2 { font-family: 'Georgia', serif; font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 400; color: #1A1208; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .page-cta p { color: #6B5A3A; font-size: 0.9rem; max-width: 540px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; line-height: 1.7; }
  .cta-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: #7A5A1A; padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500; border: 1px solid #7A5A1A; }
  .btn-secondary:hover { background: #F5EFE0; }
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .pricing-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .page-hero h1 { font-size: 1.75rem; }
    .pricing-card { padding: 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>